query: Research quantum computing hardware state in 2024-2025 for enterprise adoption. Context: Technical assessment for enterprise adoption decision. Goal: Identify top 3 quantum computing platforms by qubit count and error rates. Focus areas: 1) Hardware specifications (qubit count, coherence time, gate fidelity), 2) Error correction capabilities and recent improvements, 3) Commercial availability and pricing models. Success criteria: 3+ peer-reviewed sources per area with quantitative benchmarks. Constraints: Prioritize Nature, Science, IEEE journals and industry leaders (IBM, Google, IonQ).
